All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Comparable, DependentParameterAPI, NamedObjectAPI, ParameterAPI
public class IntegerParameter
extends DependentParameter
implements DependentParameterAPI, ParameterAPI

Title: IntegerParameter
Description: Generic Data Object that contains an Integer and optionally a min and max allowed values stored in a constraint object. If no constraint object is present then all values should be permitted.
Copyright: Copyright (c) 2001
